<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; }
        .button { background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; }
        .info-box { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>✅ Faktura uspešno poslata</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Poštovani,</p>
            
            <p>Vaša faktura je uspešno poslata u SEF sistem.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Broj fakture:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}<br>
                <strong>Kupac:</strong> {{buyerName}}<br>
                <strong>Iznos:</strong> {{totalAmount}} {{currency}}<br>
                <strong>SEF ID:</strong> {{sefId}}
            </div>
            
            <p>Status fakture možete pratiti u aplikaciji.</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="https://sef-efakture.com/invoices/{{sefId}}" class="button">
                    Pogledaj fakturu
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>SEF eFakture - Sistem za elektronske fakture</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Sva prava zadržana</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

